&lt;p/&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Third case, &lt;tt&gt;IllegalArgumentException&lt;/tt&gt; is thrown with a message, &quot;Page size must not be less than zero!&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I think these are correct result.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;However, in second case, all elements are returned with the following SQL&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p/&gt;
&lt;div id=&quot;syntaxplugin&quot; class=&quot;syntaxplugin&quot; style=&quot;border: 1px dashed #bbb; border-radius: 5px !important; overflow: auto; max-height: 30em;&quot;&gt;
